SubjectSpecial Service Medal Bar Order ‘’NATO-OTAN’’
PrecisOrder (1) Revoking Order in Council P.C. 1995-2005 of November 28, 1995; and Order in Council P.C. 2006-810 of August 29, 2006; (2) Determining as Special service any service that meets certain conditions; and (3) Specifying that the Bar that is awarded with the Special Service Medal, representing the special service referred to in paragraph (c), is to bear the NATO Star flanked by the words
